30
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:30,640
Xing, you must be happy.

31
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:33,640
Don't worry, I'm here.

32
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,240
I won't let Gao Rui hurt you again.

33
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,710
Why did you have to kill Meizhen

34
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,560
and her only son?

35
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,030
You destroyed her family.

36
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:04,120
You've already taken her company and everything.

37
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,750
Why did you still have to kill her?

38
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,540
The fact that you're both alive is my mistake.

39
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,950
If I had known today would be this troublesome,

40
00:03:14,230 --> 00:03:15,760
I never should've let you stay.

41
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,720
Speak up.

42
00:03:17,950 --> 00:03:19,130
What's the evidence you have

43
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:21,670
that I killed Shao Meizhen?

44
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:23,880
How much do you want me to pay for it?

45
00:03:25,830 --> 00:03:27,000
You don't seriously believe

46
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,920
that everything in this world

47
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,720
can be bought with money, do you?

48
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:33,510
