49
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,230
just to make yourself

50
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:36,720
what people call a rich person.

51
00:03:40,830 --> 00:03:41,440
Yes,

52
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,000
