56
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,280
Of course, I will protect my son.

57
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,390
Where did I go wrong?

58
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,550
People like you

59
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:58,230
