60
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:03,920
I killed Shao Meizhen.

61
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,630
What can you do about it?

62
00:04:06,410 --> 00:04:08,390
I can kill Li Zixing once,

63
00:04:09,070 --> 00:04:10,760
