79
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,050
Let go of me!

80
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,350
Zixing, go back!

81
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:45,920
Let go of my mom!

82
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:47,790
