83
00:04:54,110 --> 00:04:54,750
You...

84
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,480
A recording might not be proof,

85
00:04:58,110 --> 00:04:59,310
but we have witnesses.

86
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,640
We found the transfer records

87
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,870
